			<div id="Tactics">
				<h2>Tactics Cards:</h2>
				<p>Players can buy tactics cards for their cyborgs. They allow the cyborgs to behave in a certain manner advantageous to the current situation and normally provide a massive boost to a teammember.</p>
				<p>Tactic cards give the players more possibilities regarding their action points - not only move, shoot, reload, use equipment.</p>					
				<p>Equipment cards represent hardware, Tactics cards software. Tactic cards allow the cyborgs to take cover, switch places with other cyborgs, provide cover fire,
					support other cyborgs with action points, health or damage and generally provides additional actions not representable by equipment.</p>
					
